"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">The tool assess the intensity (or power) of a time-domain signal from a polysomnopragphy (PSG) file across various frequency bands.</p>\n"
